<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4390693>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Two-dimensional ordination plot for the two-morphometric parameters based on the raw data from the present study. The ellipses drawn represent distribution spaces for each species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4390693/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4390695>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Microsclere morphology in Tsitsikamma (Tsitsikamma) and T. (Clavicaulis subgen. nov.) species (not to scale): A. T. (T.) favus Samaai & Kelly, 2002; B. T. (T.) scurra Samaai & Kelly 2003; C. T. (T.) amatholensis sp. nov.; D. T. (T.) nguni Parker-Nance, 2019; E. T. (Clavicaulis) pedunculata Samaai & Kelly, 2003; F. T. (C.) madiba subgen. et sp. nov.; G. T. (C.) michaeli Parker-Nance, 2019; H. T. (C.) beukesi subgen. et sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4390695/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4390699>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Phylogram constructed from COI sequences showing family Latrunculiidae, as represented by Tsitsikamma, Latrunculia, Cyclacanthia and Sceptrella specimens, as monophyletic and resolved as separate to Tsitsikamma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4390699/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4390701>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Phylogram constructed from ITS sequences for Tsitsikamma specimens showing integrity of the two subgenera, Tsitsikamma and Clavicaulis subgen. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4390701/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

